    <item>
      <title>激进投资者 Jana 敦促保险公司 Markel 分离风险投资部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/activist-jana-pushes-insurer-markel-to-separate-venture-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据这家激进投资公司的执行合伙人斯科特·奥斯特菲尔德 (Scott Ostfeld) 称，Jana Partners 已大量购入保险公司 Markel Group Inc. 的股份，并正在敦促这家专业保险公司探索分离或出售其私人投资业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/activist-jana-pushes-insurer-markel-to-separate-venture-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:53:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lazard 首席执行官认为 2025 年将是资产管理的“转折点”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lazard-ceo-sees-2025-as-inflection-point-for-asset-management</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉扎德公司 (Lazard Inc.) 首席执行官 Peter Orszag 表示，在公司客户持有量月度出现小幅下降后，明年将成为公司资产管理业务的“转折点”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lazard-ceo-sees-2025-as-inflection-point-for-asset-management</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Voyix 称，NCR 拆分后，Atleos 被低估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/engaged-capital-says-voyix-atleos-undervalued-after-ncr-breakup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Engaged Capital 认为，如果市场没有开始正确评估这些业务，那么从 NCR Corp 中分离出来的 NCR Atleos Corp. 和 NCR Voyix Corp. 可能会吸引金融或战略买家的收购兴趣，这位激进投资者在周二的彭博激进主义论坛 2024 上表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/engaged-capital-says-voyix-atleos-undervalued-after-ncr-breakup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:58:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大立法者瞄准不透明的银行旗下支付公司 Interac</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/canadian-lawmakers-target-opaque-bank-owned-payment-firm-interac</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大立法者将矛头指向了该国广泛使用的汇款服务公司 Interac Corp. 运营的这项服务，并暗示应强制其所有者出售该服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/canadian-lawmakers-target-opaque-bank-owned-payment-firm-interac</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:48:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙计划避免举行新一轮选举，对抗法国极右翼势力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/macron-aims-to-avoid-new-french-parliament-election-before-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 寻求组建一个能执政到 2027 年的温和派联盟，从而让政府摆脱国民联盟领袖玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/macron-aims-to-avoid-new-french-parliament-election-before-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:25:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥委员会通过提高房地产税以推进预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chicago-finance-committee-advances-69-million-property-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊 (Brandon Johnson) 推进了一系列征税和收费计划，以减少房产税的增加，从而增加更多收入，使该市更接近按时通过 2025 年预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chicago-finance-committee-advances-69-million-property-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 16:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗里兰称加拿大将实现债务目标，但对赤字保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 表示，政府将继续实现逐步降低债务与国内生产总值比率的目标，但回避了有关预算赤字规模的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>焦点转向美国 CPI，新兴股市下跌，货币波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/emerging-stocks-halt-rally-as-china-momentum-starts-to-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市周二结束了连续六天的涨势，而货币交易涨跌互现，因为交易员在周三美国通胀数据公布前撤出风险较高资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/emerging-stocks-halt-rally-as-china-momentum-starts-to-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 12:14:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中国刺激政策乐观情绪抵消进口疲软影响，油价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于明年全球最大原油进口国有望出台更大胆的刺激措施，抵消了中国贸易数据的疲软，油价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 23:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街交易员屏息期待 CPI 数据：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票、债券和美元均出现小幅波动，交易员不愿进行任何重大押注，因为他们在等待关键通胀数据，以判断美联储下周是否会降息或维持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
